Class ClassSymInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • cs572.SymInfo
      • cs572.ClassSymInfo
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TypedI, TypeI

    class ClassSymInfo
extends SymInfo
implements TypedI, TypeI
    Information associated with a class. For convenience, this class allows access to the fields and methods of the class. The constructor will be null if there is no explicit constructor.
